{"tid":1821051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《本日》台灣發出民主吼聲，香港豈能繼續平靜？另外英領事件請關注","createTime":"2020-01-12T03:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T12:31:07.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dcac126cbef4a9ae28ed9ff3f8a88001b3cf4316","tid":1821051,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"台灣發出民主吼聲，香港豈能繼續平靜？<br />\n<br />\n今日，台灣人民履行普選權利，用選票與極權割蓆，捍衛民主與自由。在中共侵凌下，港台同氣連枝，台灣民主的體現，實在令港人羡慕。台灣人民在選舉後的慶祝，港人亦彷彿置身其中。<br />\n<br />\n接下來，輪到香港人繼續發聲，震撼國際。2020年將會是獨裁者面臨世界孤立的一年。明天，讓我們再次走上街頭，延續台灣人民的民主呼聲，爭取香港應得的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n1.12愛丁堡見！<br />\n<br />\nCredits to @appledailyhk<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n支持民間集會團隊（眾籌/參與）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=9affbbca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam</a><br />\n參與/洽詢合作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCATeam_bot&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=c27425eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我們的最新動向/合作洽詢：<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=c4fb4d86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=16b26a89\" data-a